- Bandit (Security): `./.venv/bin/bandit`
- Semgrep (Static Analysis): `./.venv/bin/semgrep`
- pytest (Testing): `./.venv/bin/pytest`
- Repomix (Code Packing): `npx repomix` (Node.js環境)
